114→            Learn with an
115→            <span className="block text-gradient">AI Study Buddy</span>
116→          </h1>
117→
118→          <p className="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-md text-lg text-muted-foreground lg:mx-0">
119→            Personalized guidance that adapts to your knowledge level. Get hints, not answers, and
120→            truly understand the material.
